-## Ch 6 — System Architecture [FILLED 2026-04-24]
-
-**Source:** markdown lines 2527–3008 / pdf pages ~124–150.
-**Target KB:** 5-form-function AND 7-interfaces (§6.3 non-idealities + interfaces).
