-  3. sequence_diagrams.pptx   — 4 sequence diagrams (4 slides, one per SEQ)
-
-Style: c1v brand (Firefly / Porcelain / Tangerine / Danube), 16:9, Calibri.
-Source data: n2_chart.json, data_flow_diagram.mmd, sequence_diagrams.mmd,
